text: Philip Nelson may refer to: *Philip Nelson (Wisconsin politician) (1891–?), Wisconsin state Senator from 1931 to 1943 *Philip Nelson (American football) (born 1993), American football player *Philip E. Nelson (born 1935), American food scientist *Philip Nelson-Ward (1866–1937), British Royal Navy officer and courtier *Philip Nelson (antiquarian) (1872–1953), British founder of the Nelson Collection ==See also== *Phillip Nelson (born 1929), emeritus professor in economics at SUNY Binghamton *Nelson Phillips (1873–1939), Justice of the Texas Supreme Court
title: Philip Nelson
